Import the following GPO's:
Domain Wide
  - Clear Cached Credentials
  - LSA RunAsPPL
  - Install Sysmon (ion-storm)
  - PowerShell Logging
  - Kerberos Logging
  - Disable Insecure Kerberos Encryption Types
  - Audit User Account Management
      verify with auditpol /get /category:"account management"
Workstations
  - Restrict Scripts
  - Enable AppLocker

Add Users to Protected Users group

Reroll all creds for privileged users, and reroll creds for krbtgt twice
